data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 2023-built property is a masterpiece of modern living, boasting a host of luxurious features that will take your breath away. The heart of this home is the spacious kitchen, featuring exquisite granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. It's a chef's paradise, complete with a walk-in pantry to store all your culinary delights. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living area, accented by elegant high ceilings and a custom-made decorative wall. Natural light pours in, highlighting the exceptional details that make this home one of a kind. As you step into the master bedroom, you'll be greeted by elegant tray ceilings, adding a touch of sophistication to your private retreat. The master bedroom doesn't stop there; it includes a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower and a relaxing tub. It's your personal spa-like haven. Every corner of this home has been thoughtfully designed. New light fixtures illuminate the space, creating an inviting atmosphere. With a focus on luxury, this home offers an unparalleled living experience.    Perched on a conservation lot, this property offers enhanced privacy and tranquility. The water view adds an extra layer of serenity, making it a picturesque backdrop to your daily life. Make this remarkable property your own and experience the epitome of comfort and elegance.     Its convenient location ensures easy access to all your daily needs while providing you with a serene retreat to come home to.    Your new home includes endless fun in the sun at the Metro Lagoon, an expansive aquatic paradise spanning over 5 acres! Step into a world of excitement and relaxation right at your doorstep. The Metro Lagoon offers a stunning array of water-based activities, from towering water slides that promise exhilarating thrills to playful floating obstacles that create unforgettable memories. Embrace the serene waters with kayaks and paddle boards, perfect for those looking to enjoy a leisurely, sun-soaked day or embark on aquatic adventures. This is your own personal oasis for water enthusiasts and outdoor enthusiasts alike. Living here means having the ultimate summer getaway right outside your front door, making every day feel like a vacation. Dive into the Metro Lagoon lifestyle and experience the best in outdoor living and recreational enjoyment.    Your home is more than just a place to live; it's a gateway to a world of sun, water, and fun. Welcome to a life of leisure and adventure at its finest!
